00:57:07,539 --> 00:57:08,719
[SPEAKER_00] koji auto želiš,

690
00:57:08,719 --> 00:57:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] a daj te ti kupimo stan,

691
00:57:10,840 --> 00:57:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] makni se od nas,

692
00:57:12,380 --> 00:57:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] a mi smo ti naporni.

693
00:57:13,440 --> 00:57:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] Možda to smeka faza.

694
00:57:14,519 --> 00:57:16,300
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to te mi tjeramo.

695
00:57:16,300 --> 00:57:17,699
[SPEAKER_00] Okusi život.

696
00:57:17,699 --> 00:57:20,320
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo je radit,

697
00:57:20,320 --> 00:57:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] daj,

698
00:57:21,340 --> 00:57:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] daj ono,

699
00:57:22,460 --> 00:57:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] oćiš na neko putovanje,

700
00:57:23,960 --> 00:57:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] jel bi ovo,

701
00:57:25,019 --> 00:57:26,480
[SPEAKER_00] jel bi ono stalno nešto nudila

702
00:57:26,480 --> 00:57:27,940
[SPEAKER_00] i svaki dan

703
00:57:27,940 --> 00:57:29,320
[SPEAKER_00] onda je drugi dan reka,

704
00:57:29,320 --> 00:57:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] pa kako ćeš ti takva kakva jesi

705
00:57:31,860 --> 00:57:34,059
[SPEAKER_00] sa nekom časnom iz Dalmacije,

706
00:57:34,059 --> 00:57:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] sa nekom iz Zagorja,

707
00:57:35,940 --> 00:57:38,820
[SPEAKER_00] pa što ti misliš da će one tebi sve ugađat?

708
00:57:38,820 --> 00:57:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ja ono u nju gledam,

709
00:57:41,380 --> 00:57:42,940
[SPEAKER_00] ja kažem ništa se ti za to ne brini.

710
00:57:42,940 --> 00:57:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ja pa sve nešto se bori čovjeka,

711
00:57:45,820 --> 00:57:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] mislim si što više se s njom,

712
00:57:47,119 --> 00:57:48,900
[SPEAKER_00] ono raspravlja čovjek

713
00:57:48,900 --> 00:57:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] i ulazi u taj razgovore,

714
00:57:50,519 --> 00:57:51,500
[SPEAKER_00] to je gore.

715
00:57:51,500 --> 00:57:52,780
[SPEAKER_00] I to je baš onako,

716
00:57:52,780 --> 00:57:54,780
[SPEAKER_00] Bože me oprosti,

717
00:57:54,780 --> 00:57:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] živi primjer,

718
00:57:55,519 --> 00:57:57,219
[SPEAKER_00] i danas sa napastima,

719
00:57:57,219 --> 00:57:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] kad je Sotona napastuje kroz ovo i kroz ono,

720
00:57:59,099 --> 00:58:00,099
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo kroz misli.

721
00:58:00,099 --> 00:58:02,400
[SPEAKER_00] Kad čovjek pristane na misao,

722
00:58:02,400 --> 00:58:03,619
[SPEAKER_00] zapleten je već u mrežu,

723
00:58:03,619 --> 00:58:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] gotovo je,

724
00:58:04,400 --> 00:58:06,679
[SPEAKER_00] onda se teško čupa van.

725
00:58:07,099 --> 00:58:07,820
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je bilo tada,

726
00:58:07,820 --> 00:58:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] što sam više šutila,

727
00:58:08,960 --> 00:58:09,679
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo bolje,

728
00:58:09,679 --> 00:58:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] jednom sam mi rekla,

729
00:58:10,500 --> 00:58:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] Sam se Sotona tobom koristi,

730
00:58:11,960 --> 00:58:13,739
[SPEAKER_00] dobro, pazi što govoriš.

731
00:58:13,739 --> 00:58:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jako se naljutila na mene,

732
00:58:15,619 --> 00:58:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] ali tu sam sasjekla

733
00:58:17,480 --> 00:58:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] te njezine govore

734
00:58:19,079 --> 00:58:20,559
[SPEAKER_00] i tu sam to malo primirila,

735
00:58:20,559 --> 00:58:22,699
[SPEAKER_00] jer ne znam kako bi izdržala.

736
00:58:22,699 --> 00:58:25,679
[SPEAKER_00] Osjećala sam se tada jako loše,

737
00:58:25,679 --> 00:58:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] u jednom trenutku,

738
00:58:26,599 --> 00:58:28,519
[SPEAKER_00] kada su mene moji roditelji poslali

739
00:58:28,519 --> 00:58:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] kod jednog svećenika na razgovor,

740
00:58:30,000 --> 00:58:32,739
[SPEAKER_00] da on mene popravi.

741
00:58:32,739 --> 00:58:36,760
[SPEAKER_00] Da on meni kaže što ja trebam.

742
00:58:37,099 --> 00:58:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] I ja se sjećam,

743
00:58:39,500 --> 00:58:40,699
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam došla na taj razgovor

744
00:58:40,699 --> 00:58:42,659
[SPEAKER_00] i ja sam se osjećala tako loše.

745
00:58:42,659 --> 00:58:43,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se osjećala,

746
00:58:43,659 --> 00:58:44,840
[SPEAKER_00] veljda,

747
00:58:44,840 --> 00:58:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] izdano od vlastitih roditelja,

748
00:58:46,840 --> 00:58:48,099
[SPEAKER_00] jer jer vi meni ne vjerujete.

749
00:58:48,099 --> 00:58:50,760
[SPEAKER_00] Mama je rekla da sam se zanjela.

750
00:58:50,760 --> 00:58:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam rekla,

751
00:58:51,900 --> 00:58:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] ja ako do sada,

752
00:58:52,980 --> 00:58:55,159
[SPEAKER_00] bila sam u društvu ljudi

753
00:58:55,159 --> 00:58:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji su pušili marihuanu,

754
00:58:56,340 --> 00:58:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] nikad nisam pušila marihuanu,

755
00:58:57,960 --> 00:59:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam toga stava.

756
00:59:00,019 --> 00:59:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] Moje sve djevojke,

757
00:59:01,519 --> 00:59:04,179
[SPEAKER_00] kolegice iz srednje škole,

758
00:59:04,179 --> 00:59:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] sa fakulteta,

759
00:59:05,480 --> 00:59:07,360
[SPEAKER_00] kolegice u klubu,

760
00:59:07,360 --> 00:59:08,860
[SPEAKER_00] su sve svakog petka

761
00:59:08,860 --> 00:59:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] i subota bile vani.

762
00:59:09,760 --> 00:59:10,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam.

763
00:59:10,340 --> 00:59:11,340
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo mi to ne zanima.

764
00:59:11,340 --> 00:59:12,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ja to nisam voljala.

765
00:59:12,599 --> 00:59:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem,

766
00:59:13,000 --> 00:59:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] ako tebi to nije dokaz,

767
00:59:14,159 --> 00:59:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] da ja imam svoj stav

768
00:59:15,920 --> 00:59:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] i da mi nije mogo neko

769
00:59:18,199 --> 00:59:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] nagovoriti da dođem u samostanu,

770
00:59:19,519 --> 00:59:20,739
[SPEAKER_00] ja znam da to nije

771
00:59:20,739 --> 00:59:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] jedan vikend.

772
00:59:21,800 --> 00:59:22,860
[SPEAKER_00] Da je to cijeli život.

773
00:59:22,860 --> 00:59:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] Onda rekao,

774
00:59:25,119 --> 00:59:26,400
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam šta ti je drugo dokazno.

775
00:59:26,400 --> 00:59:27,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ja misliš da mama nije

776
00:59:27,360 --> 00:59:28,699
[SPEAKER_02] tebi vjerovala

777
00:59:28,699 --> 00:59:30,360
[SPEAKER_02] ili jednostavno nije se mogla

778
00:59:30,360 --> 00:59:31,800
[SPEAKER_00] pomiriti s tvojom odlukom?

779
00:59:31,800 --> 00:59:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] Nije se mogla pomiriti.

780
00:59:33,019 --> 00:59:34,239
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je ona tražila način

781
00:59:34,239 --> 00:59:35,300
[SPEAKER_00] kako da ona mene,

782
00:59:35,300 --> 00:59:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] kako da me odvuče od toga.

783
00:59:37,960 --> 00:59:38,699
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je bilo,

784
00:59:38,699 --> 00:59:39,860
[SPEAKER_00] negovorila te Monika,

785
00:59:39,860 --> 00:59:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] časne su te,

786
00:59:41,519 --> 00:59:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] zavele,

787
00:59:43,659 --> 00:59:44,780
[SPEAKER_00] zašto taj red?

788
00:59:44,780 --> 00:59:46,360
[SPEAKER_00] Sto tisuća pitanja,

789
00:59:46,360 --> 00:59:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] samo da nekak sumnja

790
00:59:48,039 --> 00:59:49,280
[SPEAKER_00] prođe negdje.

791
00:59:49,280 --> 00:59:50,460
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je bilo,

792
00:59:50,460 --> 00:59:51,260
[SPEAKER_00] ostavit ćeš ovo,

793
00:59:51,260 --> 00:59:52,340
[SPEAKER_00] pa nećeš imat ovo,

794
00:59:52,340 --> 00:59:53,519
[SPEAKER_00] pa nećeš imat ono.

795
00:59:53,519 --> 00:59:54,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam u jednom trenutku

796
00:59:54,599 --> 00:59:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] već ono pukla.

797
00:59:55,500 --> 00:59:58,679
[SPEAKER_00] Znam da sam i ton povisila

798
00:59:58,679 --> 00:59:59,460
[SPEAKER_00] i onako sam rekla,

799
00:59:59,460 --> 01:00:01,719
[SPEAKER_00] ne zanima me ništa.

800
01:00:01,719 --> 01:00:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam da ja trebam ići.

801
01:00:04,559 --> 01:00:07,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ne vidjela više u životu svome,

802
01:00:07,219 --> 01:00:08,360
[SPEAKER_00] ni tebe, ni tatu,

803
01:00:08,360 --> 01:00:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] ni braću,

804
01:00:08,880 --> 01:00:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] ni nikoga.

805
01:00:09,460 --> 01:00:10,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ni bake,

806
01:00:10,820 --> 01:00:11,900
[SPEAKER_00] ni nikoga.

807
01:00:13,119 --> 01:00:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] Mene to ne zanima.

808
01:00:15,300 --> 01:00:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] Mene u tom trenutku,

809
01:00:18,460 --> 01:00:19,760
[SPEAKER_00] kao da sam bila zavezana

810
01:00:19,760 --> 01:00:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] s nekakvim koncima

811
01:00:20,619 --> 01:00:22,119
[SPEAKER_00] i kao da me sve vuklo.

812
01:00:22,119 --> 01:00:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] Tako sam se osjećala,

813
01:00:23,460 --> 01:00:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] kao da me vuklo,

814
01:00:24,380 --> 01:00:25,260
[SPEAKER_00] da jednostavno idem.

815
01:00:25,260 --> 01:00:26,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam znala,

816
01:00:26,159 --> 01:00:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] ja moram ići,

817
01:00:26,880 --> 01:00:27,920
[SPEAKER_00] put se mora čistiti,

818
01:00:27,920 --> 01:00:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] kako tako,

819
01:00:28,539 --> 01:00:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] bolno, ovako ili onako.

820
01:00:30,039 --> 01:00:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam u to postala

821
01:00:31,460 --> 01:00:33,139
[SPEAKER_00] toliko sigurnija i sigurnija.

822
01:00:33,139 --> 01:00:35,679
[SPEAKER_00] Taj trenutak od tog svećenika

823
01:00:35,679 --> 01:00:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam cijeli susret splakala

824
01:00:37,380 --> 01:00:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] dok sam s njim razgovarala.

825
01:00:39,199 --> 01:00:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] I on je stavio,

826
01:00:41,599 --> 01:00:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] onako me ne gledala.

827
01:00:42,579 --> 01:00:43,679
[SPEAKER_00] sa što ti plaćaš

828
01:00:43,679 --> 01:00:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] ako osjećaš poziv,

829
01:00:44,460 --> 01:00:45,260
[SPEAKER_00] trebaš biti sretna.

830
01:00:45,260 --> 01:00:46,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam u njega gledala

831
01:00:46,960 --> 01:00:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] i mislela sam,

832
01:00:47,480 --> 01:00:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] Bože dragi,

833
01:00:48,340 --> 01:00:51,179
[SPEAKER_00] jel ti mi li trebaš pomoći ili ne?

834
01:00:51,179 --> 01:00:52,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali on sam,

835
01:00:52,099 --> 01:00:53,739
[SPEAKER_00] nije on kriv.

836
01:00:53,739 --> 01:00:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio napunjen

837
01:00:55,599 --> 01:00:56,760
[SPEAKER_00] od priča od mojih roditelja.

838
01:00:56,760 --> 01:00:58,360
[SPEAKER_00] Nju su nagovorili,

839
01:00:58,360 --> 01:00:59,219
[SPEAKER_00] nju su ovo,

840
01:00:59,219 --> 01:00:59,940
[SPEAKER_00] nju su ono,

841
01:00:59,940 --> 01:01:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] nju su ono,

842
01:01:00,539 --> 01:01:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] od njihove nemoći.

843
01:01:02,800 --> 01:01:03,340
[SPEAKER_00] mozioj,

844
01:01:03,340 --> 01:01:05,340
[SPEAKER_00] da ona sad shvati

845
01:01:05,340 --> 01:01:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] da ona treba biti

846
01:01:06,460 --> 01:01:07,179
[SPEAKER_00] s nama doma.

847
01:01:07,179 --> 01:01:08,360
[SPEAKER_02] Da treba biti normalna.

848
01:01:08,360 --> 01:01:09,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ona i mama se vraćala,

849
01:01:09,519 --> 01:01:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] ko će sada nama biti svjetlo,

850
01:01:10,940 --> 01:01:12,179
[SPEAKER_00] ko će sada nama biti sunce,

851
01:01:12,179 --> 01:01:13,320
[SPEAKER_00] ko će sada nama biti nada.

852
01:01:15,320 --> 01:01:15,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam znala,

853
01:01:15,980 --> 01:01:16,139
[SPEAKER_00] ne,

854
01:01:16,139 --> 01:01:18,739
[SPEAKER_00] to je...

855
01:01:18,739 --> 01:01:20,159
[SPEAKER_02] Jesi li znala što te čekao?

856
01:01:20,159 --> 01:01:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

857
01:01:20,960 --> 01:01:23,619
[SPEAKER_00] Nije mi Monika nikad ništa rekla.

858
01:01:23,619 --> 01:01:24,440
[SPEAKER_00] To je zanimljivo.

859
01:01:24,440 --> 01:01:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam nju tek poslije zahvalila na tome.

860
01:01:27,400 --> 01:01:29,780
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi mi znala hvala ti što bi nikad ništa nisi rekla

861
01:01:29,780 --> 01:01:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] o samostanu.

862
01:01:30,480 --> 01:01:33,260
[SPEAKER_00] Tehnički stvari,

863
01:01:33,260 --> 01:01:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] što se toga tiče,

864
01:01:34,159 --> 01:01:35,579
[SPEAKER_00] što su ih sestre sve govorile,

865
01:01:35,579 --> 01:01:35,820
[SPEAKER_00] da,

866
01:01:35,820 --> 01:01:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali nikada ništa o odnosima,

867
01:01:38,500 --> 01:01:40,440
[SPEAKER_00] nikada ništa o žrtvama,

868
01:01:40,440 --> 01:01:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] koje se tamo podnose,

869
01:01:41,900 --> 01:01:44,260
[SPEAKER_00] kao redovnici općenito.

870
01:01:45,320 --> 01:01:48,500
[SPEAKER_00] Nikada ništa o nekakvim,

871
01:01:48,500 --> 01:01:49,059
[SPEAKER_00] da kažem,

872
01:01:49,059 --> 01:01:49,780
[SPEAKER_00] i težinama,

873
01:01:49,780 --> 01:01:52,019
[SPEAKER_00] čak niti posebno o radostima.

874
01:01:52,019 --> 01:01:52,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa.

875
01:01:52,659 --> 01:01:55,320
[SPEAKER_00] I sam Bog se njom poslužio

876
01:01:55,320 --> 01:01:57,179
[SPEAKER_00] da mene pusti,

877
01:01:57,179 --> 01:01:59,119
[SPEAKER_00] da sama okusim korak po korak

878
01:01:59,119 --> 01:02:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] što već trebam okusiti

879
01:02:01,619 --> 01:02:03,519
[SPEAKER_00] i što je za mene gospodin pripremio.

880
01:02:03,519 --> 01:02:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] I to mi je bilo,

881
01:02:05,380 --> 01:02:07,480
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam nju poslije više puta na tome zahvalila

882
01:02:07,480 --> 01:02:08,460
[SPEAKER_00] i ona je sama rekla,

883
01:02:08,460 --> 01:02:10,679
[SPEAKER_00] ja uopće ne znam koliko sam ja to tako uspjela,

884
01:02:10,679 --> 01:02:11,139
[SPEAKER_00] mislim,

885
01:02:11,139 --> 01:02:12,360
[SPEAKER_00] jer smo se jako,

886
01:02:12,360 --> 01:02:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] jako se družimo i prijateljci smo i danas,

887
01:02:14,539 --> 01:02:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda kažem,

888
01:02:15,320 --> 01:02:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] neko ko je prirodno da prijatelji

889
01:02:17,340 --> 01:02:18,280
[SPEAKER_00] o tome razgovaraju,

890
01:02:18,280 --> 01:02:19,599
[SPEAKER_00] ona nikada nije,

891
01:02:19,599 --> 01:02:20,800
[SPEAKER_00] nikada ništa nije rekla,

892
01:02:20,800 --> 01:02:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] niti o tom zajedničkom životu,

893
01:02:22,079 --> 01:02:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] bilo koji je sestri,

894
01:02:23,059 --> 01:02:23,659
[SPEAKER_00] o bilo čemu,

895
01:02:23,659 --> 01:02:26,440
[SPEAKER_00] tako da to je sam gospodin vodio.

896
01:02:26,440 --> 01:02:29,159
[SPEAKER_02] A kakvom si odnosu s mamom danas?

897
01:02:29,159 --> 01:02:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] Dobrom.

898
01:02:29,960 --> 01:02:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

899
01:02:30,559 --> 01:02:31,719
[SPEAKER_00] Mami je trebalo,

900
01:02:31,719 --> 01:02:33,199
